casebody.data:
Lavern R. IRWIN
v.
Juanita H. BAKER, Jewyl E. Dunn, Charles Mann, Sr. No. 585P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 25, 2005. Lavern Irwin, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Baker, Dunn & Mann.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 17th day of November 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th day of January 2005."
